 JP (Michael) Maritz woke up at around 06:00 on Friday 12 January next to Groenfontein Dairy in Kanonkop. He can be seen scratching his legs before starting to prepare his fix.  On the video you can see how he extracts blood into a syringe to mix with the heroin before injecting it into his arm. It is clear that his first fix did not do the trick as he almost immediately starts preparing a second hit. Read more stories about Middelburg’s drug addicts, like where the girls from the McDonalds robot went, in this week’s Middelburg Observer. Also read: Middelburg situated on popular drug route Heroin worth millions seized Nyaope and crime walk hand-in-hand 